Package oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource

Class SwaggerResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource.BaseResource
      • oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource.SwaggerResource

  • public class SwaggerResource
extends BaseResource
    SwaggerResource is a jaxrs resource that implements the REST api for the /operator/{version}/swagger path. It can be used to get a json swagger definition of the WebLogic operator REST api.
